OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FThe family of a 19-year-old British
OL,7,Fwoman who died in a motorcycle crash
OL,8,Fon a popular route in Vietnam has paid
OL,9,Ftribute to her, calling her
OL,10,F"beautiful, independent and very
OL,11,Ffunny".
OL,13,FOrla Wates was on a motorcycle ride on
OL,14,Fthe Ha Giang Loop in the country's
OL,15,Fnorth when she was thrown off it and
OL,16,Fhit by oncoming traffic.
OL,18,FShe later died in Hanoi's Viet Duc
OL,19,FFriendship Hospital on April 2 with
OL,20,Fher family by her side, according to
OL,21,FViet Nam News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
