PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FSpeaking to Viet Nam News, Orla's
OL,7,Fparents Andrew and Henrietta Wates
OL,8,Fsaid: "Orla was beautiful, independent
OL,9,Fand very funny, with a sharp wit.J"She
OL,10,Floved to look good and lived life to
OL,11,Fthe full."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
