PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FHer mother thanked the hospital's Dr
OL,7,FTrnh Van Dong and its ICU team for
OL,8,Fcaring for her daughter ` and said her
OL,9,Forgans had been donated to save
OL,10,Fothers, according to the outlet.
OL,12,FShe said: "At this extremely difficult
OL,13,Ftime for our family, we chose to
OL,14,Fdonate Orla's organs, as we believe
OL,15,Fthat if there were a way to give
OL,16,Fopportunity to others, this is what
OL,17,FOrla would have wanted.
OL,19,F"Knowing that she is living on through
OL,20,Fthem brings us great comfort."
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
