PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FViet Duc Friendship Hospital said the
OL,7,Fdonated organs helped save the lives
OL,8,Fof three Vietnamese patients.
OL,10,FThe hospital's director presented the
OL,11,Ffamily with a "gift of gratitude"
OL,12,Fwhile the country's Health Minister
OL,13,FDao Hong Lan sent them an appreciation
OL,14,Fletter for their "noble gesture".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,F"This noble gesture not only brings
OL,7,Flife-saving opportunities to many
OL,8,Fpatients but also conveys a profound
OL,9,Fmessage of compassion, upholding
OL,10,Fhumanitarian values, the spirit of
OL,11,Fsharing, and social responsibility
OL,12,Fthat transcends all boundaries of
OL,13,Fnation and culture," the letter read.
OL,15,F"This represents one of the first
OL,16,Fcases of multi-organ donation from a
OL,17,Fforeigner in Vietnam", it added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
