PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FIn an emotional interview during their
OL,7,Fvisit to the hospital, which was
OL,8,Fshared on the hospital's social media
OL,9,Fpage, Orla's father, a building
OL,10,Ftycoon, said: "Vietnam was a country
OL,11,Fshe loved and so to give back to
OL,12,FVietnam as well I think is very
OL,13,Fimportant for us."
OL,15,FHer mother added: "She had the best
OL,16,Ftime here ... she was loving every
OL,17,Fminute of it. So it is our way of
OL,18,Fthanking you."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
