OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FThe Ha Giang Loop is a road trip of
OL,7,Faround 350km that winds through the
OL,8,FVietnamese mountains near the border
OL,9,Fwith China.
OL,11,FIt is popular among tourists, and
OL,12,Finexperienced motorcyclists often ride
OL,13,Fpillion in a group with tour operators.
OL,15,FThe loop typically takes around three
OL,16,Fto four days on a motorcycle.
OL,18,FThe Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,19,FDevelopment Office (FCDO) confirmed
OL,20,Fits consular staff is supporting the
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
