FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775696638
OL,3,CTributes paid to British teenager
OL,4,Ckilled in Vietnam motorbike crash
OL,6,FAn FCDO spokesperson said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts are with the family and
OL,8,Ffriends of Orla Wates, following her
OL,9,Ftragic death in Vietnam.
OL,11,F"We are in touch with the local
OL,12,Fauthorities, and our consular staff
OL,13,Fare doing all they can to support
OL,14,FOrla's family at this hugely difficult
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
